sequenceDiagram
    participant Provider as Zoom/Twilio
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant SQS as Amazon SQS (Buffer)
    participant Lambda as AWS Lambda (Processor)
    participant RDS as Aurora PostgreSQL
    participant S3 as AWS S3 (Audio)

    Provider->>API: Webhook (JSON Call Log)
    API->>SQS: Push Raw JSON
    API-->>Provider: 200 OK (Instant)

    Note over SQS, Lambda: Batch Processing (20 logs per run)

    SQS->>Lambda: Trigger Batch
    Lambda->>RDS: Bulk Insert (Optimized)
    Lambda->>S3: Download & Sync Recording
    Lambda-->>Staff: WebSocket: Recording Available